headline: Travel stock earnings: What to watch for
summary: A number of travel-related stocks will report quarterly results the week of July 21, including Hilton (HLT), Wyndham (WH), and Travel+Leisure (TNL). Jefferies managing director David Katz joins Market Catalysts with Julie Hyman to share what he will be watching for.
